&lt;li&gt;Advanced features can be costly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Use Case&lt;/strong&gt;: A startup utilized HubSpot&amp;rsquo;s AI capabilities to streamline their lead nurturing process, resulting in a 25% growth in customer conversion rates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="5-google-cloud-ai"&gt;5. Google Cloud AI&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;: Google Cloud AI provides machine learning and data analytics tools for businesses looking to leverage AI for operational insights.&lt;/p&gt;
